event_name: Lindy Switch Workshop with Vicky Yeung
location: Century House, New Westminster, 620 8th St, New Westminster, BC V3M 3S2, Canada
description: Vicky Yeung is coming over from Toronto to share her Lindy Hop knowledge! This workshop will focus on becoming ambidancerous through Switch dancing, and intermediate Lindy Hop concepts. You can sign up for all of the classes, or sign up a la carte.
